org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.GRM

Interface GrService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Acquire, HwResourceService, Release, SwAccessService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcquireImpl, GrServiceImpl, HwResourceServiceImpl, ReleaseImpl, SwAccessServiceImpl

    public interface GrService
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Gr Service'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owner
    • Base Execution Specification
    • Base Behavioral Feature
    • Base Behavior
    • Base Collaboration
    • Base Collaboration Use
    See Also:
    GRMPackage.getGrService()
